### ── OFFER SERVICE (/offer) ─────────────────────────────────────────────────
### Environment: Ctrl+Shift+P → Rest Client: Switch Environment → dev
### Flow: submitOffer → approveOffer (Operator) → Order is created

### 1. Submit offer — Customer Bauer, Audi A4 (MUC)
# @name submitOffer
POST {{baseUrl}}/offer/submitOffer
Authorization: {{customerBauerAuth}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "vehicleId": "40000000-4000-4000-4000-400000000004",
  "offeredPrice": 34500.00,
  "currency": "EUR",
  "desiredPickupDate": "2026-08-01",
  "notes": "Ich biete 34.500 EUR für den Audi A4"
}

### 2. List offers — Operator
GET {{baseUrl}}/offer/Offers
Authorization: {{operatorAuth}}

### 3. List offers — Customer Bauer (own offers only)
GET {{baseUrl}}/offer/Offers
Authorization: {{customerBauerAuth}}

### 4. Approve offer — Operator
### offerId: replace with ID returned from step 1
POST {{baseUrl}}/offer/approveOffer
Authorization: {{operatorAuth}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "offerId": "REPLACE_WITH_ID"
}

### 5. Reject offer — Operator (create a new offer with submitOffer first)
POST {{baseUrl}}/offer/rejectOffer
Authorization: {{operatorAuth}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "offerId": "REPLACE_WITH_ID",
  "notes": "Preis zu niedrig — Mindestpreis 36.000 EUR"
}

### 6. Resubmit rejected offer — Customer Bauer
POST {{baseUrl}}/offer/resubmitOffer
Authorization: {{customerBauerAuth}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "offerId": "REPLACE_WITH_ID",
  "offeredPrice": 36000.00,
  "notes": "Ich akzeptiere den Mindestpreis"
}
